keyFacts: The quitclaim deed was executed on December 12, 2011.
Jeffrey E. Epstein transferred property to Laurel, Inc. for a nominal fee of ten dollars.
The property is located in Palm Beach County, Florida, specifically in El Bravo Park.
The deed includes notarized acknowledgments from two notaries public.
The document specifies that the property is not the Grantor's homestead.
